    "Finally, we converted the span annotations into TALES-QA, a dataset of standalone questions on cultural knowledge.",
    "We found that despite models misrepresenting culture in generated stories, they answer questions about cultural knowledge with surprisingly high accuracy.",
    "Positionality StatementAll members of our team either live in India or have lived in India for long periods.",
    "We all have deep familiarity with the Indian culture, including knowledge about how it may vary through the country.",
    "We used our understanding of the culture for making decisions in the study, including ensuring diversity of participants and selecting topics for stories in our study."
